data.description: Large custom home with high ceilings and open kitchen with plenty of natural light.  Great features like walk in pantry, wrap-a-round kitchen counter, two car garage and spacious covered lanai.  Front bedroom was previously renovated as an office, shared bathroom has dual sinks, paved roads, mail delivery and private water source.   Ocean views and parks are 5 to 10 min drive.  10 to 15 min drive to Pahoa town where there is shopping, dinning and supermarkets.   Part of the Hawaiian Shores Recreational Association where there is a park, pool and covered picnic area.      Annual fee is $425 and subject to change.
